Encoding_Comment: Two imported case from Saudia Arabi: A Jordanian in his sixties, who works in Saudi Arabia and who recently entered the Kingdom, was diagnosed with the virus.  The next day a MERS case was recorded for a Jordanian male (38), who has recently entered the Kingdom from abroad, the Ministry of Health reported on Wednesday.
